Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on! On a journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,ねぇ 知りたいでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:27.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,描く場所に辿り着くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Come on! ねぇ、come on! On a journey!
